This CUSTOM BUILT LUXURY home sits on 3 unrestricted acres with your own private automated gate entrance to a beautiful fountain and an oasis in-ground heated pool/jacuzzi combo! Enter the home through the grand wrought iron double doors to an expansive family room with elegant crystal chandeliers hanging from the 14 foot ceilings and a grandiose center remote controlled fireplace. From the marble/wood floors throughout to the duel master suits with coffered ceilings, this is a rare gem full of top of the line materials and upgrades that are unheard-of in todays market. Come see this beauty as it's the only one of its kind.
